  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个混合云迁移的架构图。核心场景是：本地Linux环境通过NFS把数据迁到Azure，中间用AzCopy做传输。你先帮我理一下主要组件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremLinux",
        "NFS",
        "AzCopy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那本地环境我想用一个子图来框起来，里面放NFS节点。NFS的角色是IngressController对吧？然后AzCopy作为独立节点放在子图外面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremLinux",
        "NFS",
        "subgraph"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，子图就叫OnPremLinux，标注显示为Infra_LoadBalancer。NFS在里面，类型是Infra_IngressController。AzCopy也是IngressController，但它属于云端侧，放外面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremLinux",
        "NFS",
        "AzCopy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，子图画好了。现在加连线：NFS到AzCopy是一条数据流，表示文件从本地迁出。这条线需要标注吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFS",
        "AzCopy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。反过来还有一条线：AzCopy到Files，标注成Infra_LoadBalancer，表示AzCopy把文件推到目标存储。另外再加一个Note节点做备注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
        "Files",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Note节点的类型是什么？还有Files是一个独立节点还是AzCopy的别名？我看你刚才的描述有点模糊。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Files",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Files是AzCopy连线的标注，不是独立节点。Note是独立节点，类型用Infra_RedisCache，虽然实际是备注，但按我们的命名规范来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Files",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连线画好了：AzCopy指向Files，标注Infra_LoadBalancer；NFS指向AzCopy。Note节点也加上了。不过我发现Note现在没连任何线，要挂到哪儿吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
        "Files",
        "NFS",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Note先孤立放着，做图例说明用。等等，我看你画的NFS到AzCopy的线，方向对吗？应该是NFS流出到AzCopy。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NFS",
        "AzCopy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "检查了一下，方向是对的，NFS作为源指向AzCopy。但AzCopy到Files那条线，你刚才说Files是标注，可我画成了AzCopy指向一个叫Files的节点——这不对，我改一下，把Infra_LoadBalancer作为标注文本，不生成独立节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
        "Files"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "改完我看看……对，现在AzCopy那条出线标注是Infra_LoadBalancer，没有独立的Files节点了。子图的显示名称也正确，是Infra_LoadBalancer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremLinux",
        "AzCopy",
        "Files"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "有个细节：子图叫OnPremLinux，显示为Infra_LoadBalancer；但AzCopy连线的标注也是Infra_LoadBalancer。这样同名会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremLinux",
        "Files"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不会混淆，我们的规范里Infra_LoadBalancer是通用角色标签。子图是负载均衡器集群，AzCopy推送的目标也是负载均衡后的存储入口，语义一致。最终图结构：子图OnPremLinux包含NFS，NFS连AzCopy，AzCopy出线标注Infra_LoadBalancer，外加孤立节点Note。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremLinux",
        "NFS",
        "AzCopy",
        "Note"
